reviewText:
It's all softcore, which is fine I suppose. I bought this because I just adore Penny Flame. I don't really know the smokey girl too much, but she's cute also.

Half the video doesn't include penny, or just has her leading to a transition; nothing exciting. The 1/4th part that is her is just her solo and isn't as enjoyable as other online videos haha. Nonetheless, for the price and for Penny, it was worth it lol.
